9️⃣ Important Rule

Traffic works only if both sides allow it.

Source	Destination	Result
Egress ✔	Ingress ✔	Traffic Allowed
Egress ❌	Ingress ✔	Blocked
Egress ✔	Ingress ❌	Blocked
